## **Blocker report format (required in agent response)**

When any requested repo cannot complete pull, merge, commit, or push, report a **BLOCKERS** section:

```markdown
### BLOCKERS
| Repo | Step | Issue | Conflicted files | Action needed |
|------|------|-------|------------------|---------------|
| mosc-temp | pull / release merge | Unresolved conflicts | `src/foo.tsx`, `package.json` | Manual merge decision |
| batch-jobs | push release | PR required, merge conflicts on PR | — | Resolve PR #N |

### COMPLETED (no blockers)
| Repo | Work branch | Commit | Release/PR | Status |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|--------|
| test-site | main | abc1234 | release/v1.0.0 @ abc1234 | pushed |
```

- **DO:** List every conflicted file path for unresolved merges.
- **DO:** Continue commit/push for repos with **no** blockers in the same request.
- **DON'T:** Skip reporting a failed repo silently.

